OL,3,ESTEEL REIGNGPlayStation````````````````
OL,4,BWhen we say that Steel Reign is a      
OL,5,B"tank" game, you'd automatically think 
OL,6,Bit's some sort of goldfish simulator,  
OL,7,Bwherein you choose the tank you want to
OL,8,Bput your "swimmies" in, and then       
OL,9,Bproceed to SMASH IT TO LITTLE BITS.    
OL,11,FPerhaps.                               
OL,12,F                                       
OL,13,BIn actual fact, Steel Reign concerns   
OL,14,Bitself with that other sort of "tank", 
OL,15,Bthe sci-fi, missile-firing tank.       
OL,17,FYou see, this is a shoot 'em up,       
OL,18,Fwherein you drive around the           
OL,19,Fbattlefield and shoot stuff up.        
OL,20, ``````````````````````````````````1/5``
OL,21,   B That's Total Entertainment!F400    
OL,22,B]MDBAMBER: "TEA IS LIKE VAPOUR" p152   
OL,24,AReviews  BHot topic  CTV  FGo Green    
