OL,1,R{%|l4|h4sh<|h444Qo? pp o? pp  
OL,2,Rj5s1oz%jwsjk5Q #//#xt#//#xt
OL,3,ESTEEL REIGNGPlayStation````````````````
OL,4,BThe actual structure of Steel Reign    
OL,5,Bisn't exactly new. At the beginning of 
OL,6,Beach mission, you're given a number of 
OL,7,Bobjectives. Don't expect these to be   
OL,8,Bany more complex than "you must destroy
OL,9,Bsomething".                            
OL,11,FHowever, your initial reaction upon    
OL,12,Ffirst playing will be one of surprise: 
OL,13,Fthe nice, full-screen 3D environment is
OL,14,Fsplendidly detailed.                   
OL,16,BYet once you get your tank rolling,    
OL,17,Byou'll be appalled by the low frame    
OL,18,Brate, sluggish control, and            
OL,19,Bridiculously inaccurate radar.         
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````2/5``
OL,21, B Green "Gordon"F160B"Fizzy" PopF480   
OL,22,B]MDDOCTOR, MY HEALTH IS REAL BAD p198  
OL,24,AReviews  BHot topic  CTV  FGo Green    
