OL,1,R{%|l4|h4sh<|h444Qo? pp o? pp  
OL,2,Rj5s1oz%jwsjk5Q #//#xt#//#xt
OL,3,ESTEEL REIGNGPlayStation````````````````
OL,4,BThe ten or so levels in Steel Reign,   
OL,5,Band its two-player mode, had a great   
OL,6,Bdeal of potential.                     
OL,8,FThe graphics are, at times, quite nice;
OL,9,Fhelicopters swoop overhead, troops     
OL,10,Fcrouch before firing at your tank, and 
OL,11,Fthe various exploding vehicles and     
OL,12,Fbuildings will make you smile.         
OL,14,BUnfortunately, lining yourself up to   
OL,15,Bshoot, and simply reaching your        
OL,16,Bobjective, is let down by the clunky   
OL,17,Bgraphics, unforgiving controls, and    
OL,18,Bgeneral lack of inspiration. It's so   
OL,19,Bnearly good, it hurts.                 
